Revlon, Inc. is an American multinational cosmetics, skin care, fragrance, and personal care company founded in 1932 and based in New York City.



Contents


1 History

1.1 Founding and Charles Revson control (1932-1975)
1.2 Michel Begerac control (1975-1985)
1.3 Ronald Perelman control (1985-present)


